channel.title: The Hunt For Mapdata
channel.description:
Hey guys, it's come into my interest lately that I find more mapdata pieces that I may not already have so that I can have a near-full Dungeoneering map spectrum. I provided an image of what I already don't have. If you have any map data pieces from 602+, can you please post that here or upload it so I can check to see if it has any of these missing sections that I need. I appreciate it.
I have nearly all the regions for the frozen floor, and then all of the regions up to occlude. I don't know if the update came out after December of last year.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/5LFwx.png[/img]
If you're interested in creating a map like this from your cache here are the files for doing that, it'll work on any revision before protocol 7 for the children tables came out.
http://www.mediafire.com/?vd0x3w4cs3qa20v
